'''Hangar Bay 1271''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|hangar bay]] on the original [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]]. [[Atour Riten]] docked the ''[[Nordieus]]'' there during the final stages of the Death Star's construction at [[Despayre]].<ref name="DSn">[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref> It was destroyed when the Death Star exploded in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]].<ref name="Episode IV">{{Film|IV}}</ref>

